WEBVTT

00:03:27.400 --> 00:03:30.096
And I was always secretly hoping
in some part of me

00:03:30.120 --> 00:03:32.760
that what was being said to me
and about me wasn't ...

00:03:34.240 --> 00:03:35.440
true.

00:03:37.040 --> 00:03:39.136
Because even I,

00:03:39.160 --> 00:03:42.320
an avowed, self-declared feminist,

00:03:43.240 --> 00:03:45.320
who worships at the altar of Gloria --

00:03:46.000 --> 00:03:47.440
(Laughter)

00:03:48.440 --> 00:03:50.120
internalize the patriarchy.

00:03:51.000 --> 00:03:52.536
This is really critical.

00:03:52.560 --> 00:03:55.336
Patriarchy is not boys and men.

00:03:55.360 --> 00:03:58.096
It is a system
in which we all participate,

00:03:58.120 --> 00:03:59.320
including me.